title: Data Masking UDRs - MediationZone Documentation 9.4 - InfoZone
text: The Data Masking agent has one UDR type; LookupFailure Open This UDR is routed on the selected route when you select the Route Error option in the Data Masking agent configuration. Field Description Field Description Messages (list<string>) This field contains a list of the error messages. UDR (DRUDR) These are the unmatching UDRs.
